plot: Tricked into a trap by use of a fresh brain lure, Murphy is captured by an overly enthusiastic and slightly unbalanced zombie fan, "The Collector," who is hell-bent on adding him to his zombie museum. Murphy must match wits with the Collector if he's to survive, much less escape.

Murphy is caught in a trap by an insane zombie collector and taken to his house where he shows his collection of zombies. He wears an electric necklace in Murphy to control him and wants to drain his blood. Meanwhile the survivors split to seek out Murphy and 10K suspects of the owner of the house where Murphy is arrested. He sneaks inside the house, but is captured by The Collector that wants to force Murphy to bite 10k. What will happen to him?—Claudio Carvalho, Rio de Janeiro, Brazil
